        <h3>
          Jane Bennett Accredited by Solicitors for the Elderly
        </h3>
        <p class="date">
          6th October 2016 by <span>Jane Bennett</span>
         
        </p>Having passed the appropriate qualifying modules and criteria, Jane Bennett is now a fully Accredited member of Solicitors for the Elderly (SFE). The SFE give the following 10 reasons why it's a smart move to use an Accredited Lawyer<br>

<a href="/documents/10 reasons to use an SFE accredited lawyer.pdf" class="button">Reasons to use an SFE Accredited Lawyer </a>
      
       
