        <h3>
          JE Bennett at the wings for life run in Cambridge
        </h3>
        <p class="date">
          20th April 2016 by <span>Jane Bennett</span>
        </p>
        <p>
          The team are heading to Cambridge on May 8th to take part in the Wings for Life World Run <br> <a href="http://www.wingsforlifeworldrun.com/gb/en/cambridge/" class="button">wings for life</a> <br> For most of us, training has been brief, so wish us luck, we'll need it! Obviously, it's all in a good cause, raising money to help those with spinal cord injuries. Here is a link to our just giving page:
